            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>unoni</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>R</abbr><ex>eginae</ex></expan></supplied> et <expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>enio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>oci</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Pompeius <lb n="3"/>Gratinus <lb n="4"/>miles <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>VIII <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>pro se et su<lb break="no" n="8"/>is <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratore</ex></expan> Com<lb break="no" n="9"/>modo II et <lb n="10"/>Vero II co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Vermutlich verschleppt aus Jagsthausen. Inschrift ausgemalt, verwitterter Zustand; auf rechter und linker Seite Ornamente. Autopsie R. Wiegels. Hauptbearbeiterin B. Esch.</p>
            </div>
